<%- include("../partials/header", { title: page.pageTitle }) %>

<style>
  /* ===== Container Styling ===== */
  .rp-container {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0d1b2a;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .rp-section-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #0d1b2a;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* ✅ Changed underline to green */
  .rp-section-title::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    height: 3px;
    width: 50%;
    background: #84cc16; /* Green underline */
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .investigator-card {
    background: #e9f5e1;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .investigator-card img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .money-box {
    background: #d9f99d;
    padding: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #065f46;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .team-table {
    background: #f9fafc;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .team-table h6 {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0d1b2a;
  }

  .impact-list li {
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
</style>

<div class="container py-4 rp-container">
  <h1>Research Funded Project Highlight</h1>

  <div class="row">

    <!-- LEFT COLUMN -->
    <div class="col-md-4">

      <div class="investigator-card">
        <img src="/images/mukesh.jpg" alt="Dr Mukesh">
        <strong>Dr. M. B. Mukesh Krishnan</strong><br>
        Professor, NWC, SRMIST
      </div>

      <div class="investigator-card">
        <img src="/images/suresh.jpg" alt="Dr Suresh">
        <strong>Dr. A. Suresh</strong><br>
        Professor, NWC, SRMIST
      </div>

      <div class="money-box">
        Sanctioned Amount <br>
        ₹ 88.4 Lakhs
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT COLUMN -->
    <div class="col-md-8">

      <p>
        The Department of Networking and Communications proudly announces the sanction 
        of a prestigious funded research project under a national funding scheme, 
        reflecting the department’s strong focus on interdisciplinary research, 
        healthcare technologies, and explainable AI systems.
      </p>

      <p><strong>Project Title:</strong><br>
        Explainable AI-Based Clinical Decision Support Service for Hospitals and Telemedicine Platforms.
      </p>

      <h5 class="rp-section-title">Principal Investigators</h5>

      <div class="row team-table">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h6>Indian Team</h6>
          <p><strong>PI:</strong> Dr. M.B Mukesh Krishnan,<br> SRM Institute of Science and Technology.</p>
          <p><strong>Co-PI:</strong> Dr. A. Suresh,<br> SRM Institute of Science and Technology.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h6>International Team</h6>
          <p><strong>PI:</strong> Dr. Lipo Wang,<br> Nanyang Technological University, Singapore.</p>
          <p><strong>Co-PI:</strong> Dr. Eric Peng Huat Yap,<br> Nanyang Technological University, Singapore.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-3"><strong>Funding Agency:</strong>  
        SPARC (Scheme for Promotion of Academic and Research Collaboration)
      </p>

      <p><strong>Project Duration:</strong>  
        November 2025 – October 2027 (2 Years)
      </p>

      <h5 class="rp-section-title">Project Significance</h5>

      <p>
        This project aims to develop an Explainable Artificial Intelligence (XAI) driven 
        clinical decision support framework that enhances transparency, trust, and reliability 
        in hospital workflows and telemedicine platforms. By integrating networking technologies, 
        AI interpretability, and secure data communication, the project aligns with the department’s 
        vision of advancing intelligent, ethical, and scalable healthcare systems.
      </p>

      <h5 class="rp-section-title">Departmental Impact</h5>

      <ul class="impact-list">
        <li>Research leadership in AI-driven networked healthcare systems</li>
        <li>Industry-academia collaboration under national initiatives</li>
        <li>Opportunities for student involvement, publications, and technology transfer</li>
        <li>The Department congratulates the investigators and looks forward to impactful outcomes from this funded research initiative.</li>
      </ul>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include("../partials/footer") %>